    <stitle>HOOD, GRILLE, FENDERS AND BUMPER - 8600 - ADJUSTMENTS - Fog Light - Removal</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="2">
        <title>Fog Light - Removal</title>
        <para>The fog lights are located at the center opening (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0900861">Figure 61, Item 1</hotlnk>) of the front bumper assembly.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tilt the hood forward.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the fog light assembly harness and connection.</para>
            <figure id="f0900861" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figg09/G0900861.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                         scalefitheight="272px"/>
                <caption>Figure 61. Chassis Fog Lights</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. FOG LIGHT LOCATION</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="f0900862" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figg09/G0900862.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                         scalefitheight="272px"/>
                <caption>Figure 62. Fog Light Removal</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. FOG LIGHT HARNESS</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. VERTICAL ADJUSTMENT</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. LENS COVER RETAINER SCREW</callout1>
                    <callout1>4. CROSS BAR</callout1>
                    <callout1>5. FOG LIGHT MOUNTING FLAT WASHER AND LOCK NUT</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Disconnect the harness from hood harness.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Loosen and remove fog light mounting nut and flat washer (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0900862">Figure 62, Item 5</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove fog light assembly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate and remove lens ring screws (
                <hotlnk document="s09008_25.xml" xrefid="f0900863">Figure 63, Item 3</hotlnk>) to gain access to fog
                light bulb.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the bulb and replace if required.</para>
            <para>Follow same procedure for removal of opposite side fog light.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
